<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #104c57 0%, #ff914d 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .booking-details { background: white; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #ff914d; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Luxé TimeTravel</h1>
            <h2>Booking Confirmation</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for booking with Luxé TimeTravel! Your booking has been confirmed.</p>
            
            <div class="booking-details">
                <h3>Booking Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Booking Code:</strong> {{bookingCode}}</p>
                <p><strong>Tour/Experience:</strong> {{productTitle}}</p>
                <p><strong>Package:</strong> {{packageName}}</p>
                {{#if timeSlot}}<p><strong>Time Slot:</strong> {{timeSlot}}</p>{{/if}}
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{bookingDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Participants:</strong> {{adults}} Adults{{#if children}}, {{children}} Children{{/if}}</p>
                {{#if amountPaid}}
                  <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> ₹{{amountPaid}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <p>We will send you a detailed voucher once your payment is confirmed. Please keep this booking code for your records.</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us:</p>
            <p>Email: {{companyEmail}}<br>Phone: {{companyPhone}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing {{companyName}}!</p>
            <p>Discover the Extraordinary</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>